cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.AI, cs.CV

The paper focuses on congestion control for real-time video communication, which is a networking problem. Therefore, cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category. The paper also mentions the use of statistical learning, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.IT (Information Theory), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed method in terms of video quality, which falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision).
